OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday breezy with showers.
OL,7,FBecoming more settled on Thursday with
OL,8,Fonly the odd isolated shower. A dry
OL,9,Fand warm sunny day on Friday.
OL,10,FTemperatures near average, trending
OL,11,Fupwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
